title: Ep 143: Not Feeling Good Enough
description: In this episode I get deep on relief vs. joy and not feeling good enough. Also, why do we get scared going into new goals and experiences? An emailer asks if he should have children because he is freaked out over not being good enough. A friend of the podcast writes in asking if he should take his dream job. An artist writes in asking how to monetize his business. It's all about not feeling good enough. Get your life! Let's feel good about ourselves.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
